<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Amount</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the full or partial amount that you want to book.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Credit/Debit</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select <strong>Credit</strong> or <strong>Debit</strong>. The selection depends on the pending amount. <strong>Credit</strong> is selected by default. <strong>Debit</strong> is selected for negative pending amounts, e.g. overpaid payments. This selection can be changed if needed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Currency</strong></p></td>
