<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Assignment</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select <strong>Assigned</strong>, <strong>Unassigned</strong> or <strong>ALL</strong>.<br>
<strong>Assigned</strong> = Only payments assigned to an order will be displayed.<br>
<strong>Unassigned</strong> = Only payments not assigned to an order will be displayed.</p></td>
